title: (video) (Concert) Jimi Hendrix - Live @ The Royal Albert Hall -
description: The Last Experience Concert: Live at the Royal Albert Hall is a live album containing Jimi Hendrix&#039;s performance with the Experience at the Royal Albert Hall, on February 24, 1969. The concert was filmed and recorded, because it was planned to be released as a movie, Experience. The movie has never seen an official release, but there are many packagings of the audio recording. This one was released in 1990.
